thread.title_full: Super Store 4 Less reviewed by Charles

author: Charles
title: Charles
text:
Great seller. Item was shipped out quickly and was exactly what I expected at a great price. It is not always easy to know if you can trust a seller, but Super Store 4 Less is one you can trust. I ordered a new battery for my camera and they send an actual new Canon OEM battery, not some knock-off.
I would definitely recommend them without reservation!
